* Anyone can sponsor as many facts as they want using any payment method they want. Simply send an email to breck@pldb.com with how many facts you'd like to sponsor on what language(s). For an example of a language with sponsored facts, see <a href="https://pldb.com/languages/markdown.html">Markdown</a>.

subsection Terms

* Sponsor a fact(s) and PLDB will prioritize research into this language or column type. If you are not 100% satisfied with the research that is done you can request a full refund, no questions asked with no expiration.